  "rationale": "The page follows the brief's arc \u2014 reveal, what shipped, who believes it, the ask. The hero reuses hero-photo-overlay with the sanctioned text-on-media display title (centered, so no counterweight needed). The what-shipped reveal renders as four parallel product cards, one agent per job, each bound to its real product icon. The beta-proof band renders the three launch numbers as a clean grid. The testimonial is a single centered pull-quote in list-rows form with NO declared asymmetric anchor (the sec-4 alignment-resolution failure is fixed by omitting the anchor so it resolves through the header grammar rather than declaring 'left' without a counterweight). The close reuses closing-cta-dark on the licensed deep-teal band with a single primary and a quiet secondary. All headings are sentence case, no uppercase, no exclamation marks, accent stays on controls only."
